OL,3,CHomeowner issues warning after kitchen
OL,4,Cdestroyed by fire
OL,6,FA homeowner in Kent whose kitchen was
OL,7,Fdestroyed by a fire is urging people
OL,8,Fto turn off their electrical
OL,9,Fappliances when they aren't in use.
OL,11,FSaid Boumara from Tunbridge Wells
OL,12,Freceived a phone call from his
OL,13,Fneighbour to say his house was on fire
OL,14,Fin September last year.
OL,16,FWhen he returned to his house on
OL,17,FRedleaf Close, crews from Kent Fire
OL,18,Fand Rescue Service were tackling the
OL,19,Fflames.
