OL,6,FIt is believed the fire was accidental
OL,7,Fand started by a faulty hot water
OL,8,Fdispenser plugged in on the kitchen
OL,9,Fcounter.
OL,11,FThe kitchen was destroyed and the
OL,12,Fsmoke damage impacted the whole house.
OL,14,FMr Boumara said: "As much as you
OL,15,Flisten to the advice, you never think
OL,16,Fit's going to happen to you.
