OL,6,F"Now when I leave the house, I make
OL,7,Fsure everything's switched off at the
OL,8,Fplug, I make sure the doors are
OL,9,Fclosed, and I test my smoke alarms
OL,10,Fevery week."
OL,12,FFirefighters were able to find three
OL,13,Fof Mr Boumara's cats who were given
OL,14,Fpet oxygen and passed onto the vets.
OL,16,FTwo of them have since made a full
OL,17,Frecovery but one died.
