OL,6,FMr Boumara said: "I just wanted my
OL,7,Fcats found and the crews were talking
OL,8,Fto me the whole time and telling me
OL,9,Fwhat they were doing, reassuring me.
OL,11,F"I didn't realise they had oxygen for
OL,12,Fpets, and I am so grateful to the
OL,13,Ffirefighters, and the vets, for doing
OL,14,Fwhat they could to save them."
OL,16,FIain, Station Leader at Tunbridge
OL,17,FWells, said: "The crews worked
OL,18,Fincredibly hard, and incredibly
OL,19,Fquickly.
