OL,6,F"We used very aggressive firefighting
OL,7,Ftactics."
OL,9,FHe added: "The smoke was so hot that
OL,10,Fit melted the smoke alarms in the
OL,11,Fhallway.
OL,13,F"But the rooms with the least damage
OL,14,Fare the ones where the doors were
OL,15,Fclosed.
OL,17,F"If you're going out for the day and
OL,18,Fyour electrical item doesn't need to
OL,19,Fbe on, then turn it off. It's not
OL,20,Fworth the risk."
